H0.text: What was the name of the Prime Minister of Egypt who was assassinated in 1910. Muhammad Said Pasha

H1.text: What was the name of the Prime Minister of Egypt who was assassinated in 1910. Hussein Rushdi Pasha

H2.text: What was the name of the Prime Minister of Egypt who was assassinated in 1910. Mustafa Fahmi Pasha

H3.text: What was the name of the Prime Minister of Egypt who was assassinated in 1910. Boutros Ghali

A4.text: Ghali was shot by Ibrahim Nassif al-Wardani on 20 February 1910, and died a day later, on 21 February.

A5.text: Ghali died in office on 21 February 1910 and was replaced by Muhammad Said Pasha.
